There is something wrong with the `ModelBuilder.createArrow()` method. The `camera` is at `(0,0,0)`, its direction is `(0,0,1)`, its near clipping distance is `0.1` and its far clipping distance is `10000`. The below code:

```
modelBatch.begin(camera);
Model m = modelBuilder.createArrow(20f,20f,100, -20f,-20f,200, 0.1f, 0.1f, 5, 
    GL20.GL_TRIANGLES, new Material(ColorAttribute.createDiffuse(Color.RED)),
    Usage.Position | Usage.Normal);
ModelInstance mi = new ModelInstance(m);
modelBatch.render(mi);
modelBatch.end();
```

